 Calamari Salad 1 lettuce 2 tomatoes sliced 1 cucumber sliced 1 onion sliced 250 g calamari tubes 2 tbs lemon juice 1 tbs Cajun spice 2 tbs olive oil Dressing ¼ cup red wine vinegar 3 tbs olive oil 1 tsp honey ½ tsp Italian herbs Salt and pepper  Method Place calamari in lemon juice for 10 minutes. Strain lemon juice, sprinkle Cajun spice over calamari. Heat oil to a hot temperature, fry calamari in small batches until they turn matt white, about 1 minute. Layer lettuce, cucumber, onions finish with calamari, drizzle dressing. Dressing Mix all ingredients together. The Saturday Star